data.title: The Uncanny (film)
data.text:
The Uncanny is a 1977 film about a horror author who tells three stories about killer cats.

Directed by Claude Héroux. Written by Michael Parry.

Cats aren't always cute and cuddly! (taglines)

Dialogue

[edit]

Angela: Lucy, please make me big again. I won't tell Mommy about the cat. I won't tell her about anything. Lucy, please! I promise!

Lucy: You're not such a big girl anymore, are you, Angela? Why, you're no bigger than a mouse!

Taglines

[edit]

A trilogy of feline terror!

They prowl by night...lusting for human flesh!

Cats aren't always cute and cuddly!
